    "In total, the procedure has spacetime allocation O( 2n + (n -m)2 n-m) (SA approx = O(2 n log(n/ϵ) + (n -m)2 n-m)).Adding both parts together, the SP+CSP protocolachieves depth O(n) (D approx = O(n + log(1/ϵ)) and has spacetime allocation O(m2 m + 2 n + (n -m)2 n-m) (SA approx = O(m2 m + 2 n log(n/ϵ) + (n -m)2 n-m)).If m is chosen such that⌈log 2 (n)⌉ ≤ m ≤ ⌊n -log 2 (n)⌋, (17)we see that the stated result of spacetime allocationO(2 n) (SA approx = O(2 n log(n/ϵ))) is true.",
